  <div id='content'>
    <p id='introduction'>jQuery-busy is a <a href='http://jquery.com/'>jQuery</a> plugin which allows to effortlessy show or hide animated activity / busyness indicator (call it spinner, loader or however you wish).</p>

    <a name='features'></a>
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <div class='section features'>
      <ul>
        <li><span>very easy to use</span></li>
